OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Finto the evening, although a little
OL,7,Frain or drizzle perhaps fringing the
OL,8,Fsouth. Staying rather cloudy and murky
OL,9,Fgenerally, although some limited cloud
OL,10,Fbreaks may develop in the north to
OL,11,Fallow a frost and fog in places later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FRather cloudy, with the odd
OL,14,Fspot of rain or drizzle in the west
OL,15,Fespecially. Brightest in the east,
OL,16,Fwith the best chance of some eventual
OL,17,Flimited brighter intervals. Light
OL,18,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
